  "descriptionParagraphs": [
    "The #77+ from SHARPEYE Surfboards delivers the world's fastest surfboard with Superior Performance in Serious Conditions.",
    "Based on the 2022/23 World Champion Filipe Toledo's #77 model, the #77+ has been updated for 2025. Based on team rider feedback, the deep single concave has been replaced with a slight single-to-double concave, providing enhanced hold and tighter turns in bigger, more powerful waves.",
    "The #77+ features a full entry and exit rocker, sensitive low rails for maximum control and bite, and a speed-generating slight single concave that flows into a double between the fins. The deepest point of the concave is positioned between the fins providing an abundance of drive and grip through high-speed manoeuvres in plus-sized conditions. With added forward volume, the #77+ is the ideal model for additional paddle power in conditions of consequence. The #77+ offers Superior Performance in Serious Conditions and is recommended only for intermediate to expert surfers.",
    "Looking for Superior Performance in Serious Conditions, choose the #77+. We recommend riding the #77+ in the same width as your go-to shortboard with increased thickness."
  ],
